Class JSWrapper

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--FESI.Data.JSWrapper
Direct Known Subclasses:
JSGlobalWrapper
public class JSWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements JSObject

Package an EcmaScript object as a JSObject for use by the Netscape like interface.

                                      JSFunction jsf)
